Package: smartReports
Version: 0.3.3
Title: Comprehensive Report Generation with Enhanced Plots and Tables
Description: The smartReports package provides comprehensive tools for generating professional and customizable reports in R. It offers advanced functions to create high-quality plots and well-formatted tables effortlessly. It streamlines the process of data visualization and presentation, allowing users to build detailed reports that combine insightful graphics and tables seamlessly. It integrates Quarto for multi-format rendering (HTML/PDF/DOCX) with configurable templates.
